N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 3 ยง 402.20 - Reports of misconduct

State Regulations

Every licensee shall submit a report to the superintendent
immediately upon the discovery of any of the events listed in Part 300 of this

Title. Such report shall be submitted as set forth in Part 300 of this
